	<Text>Look at blinking button on Button Panel. This is &quot;Ambush&quot; command. Units at the &quot;Ambush&quot; state will attack the enemy, only after having been detected by it. In some cases this allows them to attack first, that grants certain bonus over the enemy.
Ambush is a first special ability available for medium tanks. There are four slots for units&apos; special abilities. Different unit types has different abilities.
Set the tanks in &quot;Ambush&quot; state.</Text>
